{"tid":1289556,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大家小心]九龍大遊行小心唔好衝擊！","createTime":"2019-07-06T06:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T10:44:38.000Z","uid":264676,"like":44,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9cc2e35d7c8d409c401330fac0a1eb789a51bfa4","tid":1289556,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:59:26.000Z","msg":"樓下呢個Post可見，絕大部分巴絲贊成聽日遊行係<strong>和理非回合</strong>：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1287640\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1287640</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>衝絕對唔等於係鬼，<br />\n不過既然今次講明係和平示威，<br />\n為咗達到輿論效果，<br />\n希望手足謹記不流血、不被捕、不受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n相信大家都聽過有人想搞事，營造我哋好撚暴力嘅壞形象，如果係真嘅話，咁對家真係好撚老套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但都記得如果聽日遇到呢啲可疑人物，佢哋一出手就要小心，大家臨場應變：<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_679423_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_679423_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjZqf9GMxMWJW6noFhHuW3mc%3D&h=29caf861\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_679423_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b8b1580e\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_679423_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"61cd0772cbd82e4681a9c7b043c297c7e3fdde7a","tid":1289556,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AmXes9S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmXes9S.png&h=e2fbbade&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30d8d6442f90c59a777215d9df60093ed2a97676","tid":1289556,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"【小心黑社會】江湖傳聞指黑幫收錢行動 派古惑仔混入抹黑抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_679423_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_679423_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjZqf9GMxMWJW6noFhHuW3mc%3D&h=29caf861\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_679423_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b8b1580e\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_679423_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n反送中示威已經持續一個月，由於特區政府完全沒有回應市民的訴求，前日，抗爭人士就將行動升級。不過，最令人擔憂的是，有江湖消息指出，有黑社會份子已經混入示威群眾。跟14年雨傘革命一樣，企圖抹黑整個運動。<br />\n<br />\n有江湖人士向本刊說，由於今次反送中示威遲遲未能平息，而且民意一直在抗爭者一方，有富豪為向內地獻媚，於是擲了一筆維穩費，請來黑幫社團幫手。有消息說，黑幫14K和新義安，已經接了指示行動，派出古惑仔混入抗爭人群，再乘機生事，抹黑一班抗爭年青人。<br />\n<br />\n6月30日的撐警活動，有傳媒就揭發，號稱新義安總管的林江，事前在社交平台號召，要求旗下門生出席撐警活動。當日，新義安尖沙咀頭目家輝，就率領一大班古惑仔到場撐警。<br />\n<br />\n7月1日早上，本刊在立法會大樓附近的愛丁堡廣場，發現十多名穿上黑色上衣的金毛紋身古惑仔聚集。他們一到場，就立即戴上黑色口罩，看上去跟反送中抗爭者很相似。之後，其中一名疑似頭目的古惑仔，用手機跟對方說，他們已到齊等候指示。之後，這班人去了立法會大樓，再各自混入人群中。<br />\n<br />\n其後，有網民在社交平台表示，前日立法會大樓外，有人借機生事。網民還上載照片，說搞事那班人，就是活躍尖沙咀的新義安古惑仔。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有反對派前日亦受到黑社會襲擊。人民力量在銅鑼灣崇光百貨門口的街站，被一批古惑仔搗亂生事，有示威者阻止時，更被人打到骨折。<br />\n<br />\n內地為打壓香港的反對聲音，往往喜歡利用黑勢力。好像14年雨傘運動期間，除了多個佔領區都先後受到古惑仔衝擊外，更有黑社會圍堵壹傳媒大樓。14年10月時，有黑幫和勝和背景的元朗古惑仔竇雞學和大頭文，帶領大批人馬來到將軍澳壹傳媒大樓外生事，還大大聲喊打喊殺。<br />\n<br />\n除了黑社會，內地還會要求本地的同鄉會組織，出手狙擊反對人士。14年10月雨傘運動期間，多個同鄉會組職都有動員狙擊佔領人士。其中汕尾市陸河海外聯誼總會，更是當中表表者。因為該會會長范振聲，曾經親自帶隊，率領數百名鄉音大叔大媽，來圍堵壹傳媒大樓，指罵出入的員工。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以，一班反送中的抗爭者，真的要小心，提防有黑幫份子假扮同路人，從中抹黑整個運動。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"139010c157e8cf59c108562037a65cf8a3184d19","tid":1289556,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58a4a241763f708ebf7d58214c8637272f86066e","tid":1289556,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:03:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca2327fc6ce391dacacd5cfdf887cb387af7622f","tid":1289556,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:04:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"008b024b6711610a7e82d64ba06704c207eef6a3","tid":1289556,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64b51df6d9ff433c74405c97d5b3cf0c78b7a326","tid":1289556,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:04:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"779764b76727ed3120b0ca0cea5bba60f7189721","tid":1289556,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b7b294a41fc41f692afae311306a8672ef2e468","tid":1289556,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20